OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy and breezy on
OL,6,FSaturday with a few spots of light
OL,7,Frain in north Devon and Cornwall.
OL,8,FDrier elsewhere, but still largely
OL,9,Fcloudy. A few brighter spells likely
OL,10,Fin the east where it will feel warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying cloudy tonight with
OL,13,Fsome light rain and drizzle continuing
OL,14,Fover the hills. Drier elsewhere,
OL,15,Fperhaps with a few clearer spells to
OL,16,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
