OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAfter a cloudy start, cloud
OL,6,Fwill start to lift and break through
OL,7,Fthe morning. Prolonged sunny spells
OL,8,Fwill develop with some warm sunshine
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,12,Fstart from next week with increasing
OL,13,Famounts of sunny spells. Staying
OL,14,Flargely dry with warm sunshine and
OL,15,Flighter winds.
